@startuml
title Bridge

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Decouple an abstraction from its implementation so both can vary independently.

**Use when**: Need to avoid a combinatorial explosion of subclasses (e.g., shapes vs. rendering APIs).

**Key participants**: Abstraction, RefinedAbstraction, Implementor, ConcreteImplementor.
endlegend

interface Implementor {
  +operationImpl()
}

class ConcreteImplementorA
class ConcreteImplementorB
Implementor <|.. ConcreteImplementorA
Implementor <|.. ConcreteImplementorB

abstract class Abstraction {
  -impl : Implementor
  +operation()
}
class RefinedAbstraction

Abstraction <|-- RefinedAbstraction
Abstraction o-- Implementor
@enduml